package com.syncura360.dto.Drug
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    com.syncura360.dto
    Defines Data Transfer Objects (DTOs) used for carrying data between layers or across API boundaries.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    DrugDeletionDTO
    DTO for deleting a drug, containing the required National Drug Code (NDC).
    DrugFetchDTO
    DTO for fetching drug details, including NDC, name, category, description, strength, and pricing information.
    DrugFetchListDTO
    DTO that contains a list of drug details (DrugFetchDTO) for fetching multiple drugs.
    DrugFormDTO
    DTO for submitting a new drug with details such as NDC, name, category, description, strength, pricing, and quantity information.
    DrugUpdateDTO
    DTO for updating an existing drug's details such as NDC, quantity, and price information.
